    - 3.8: move rc2 support to rc4
    - 3.8: APF51: fix default config so that DTB is bootable
    - 2.6.35: APF28: disable by default DMA mode for Application UART - DMA mode may be source of extra delays with communication based on too few amount of bytes : terminal, GPS, GSM/GPRS..
    - [3.8] imx-fb: fix imxfb_info configuration order
    - [3.8] imx-fb: modifies platform device name
