    - [2010.11] Patch 052 wasn't right
    - [2010.11] Add link for apf9328 Linux 2.6.29.6 config
    - [2010.11] Makes ch70241ctrl compile OK
    - [2010.11] Makes U-Boot & Linux version detected correctly in ARMADEUS_xx envt variables
    - [2010.11] Removes unneeded patches 049 & 050
    - [2010.11] u-boot: makes the resulting binary copied with the right name in output/images/
    - [2010.11] u-boot: makes u-boot.mk use the right config file for apf* (apf memory config wasn't taken into account before this change)
    - [2010.11] Merge 051i U-Boot patch into 051d. Both patches apply on the same purpose
    - [2010.05] Upgrade to soon coming 2010.11 (part 4: update Armadeus main Makefile
    - [2010.05] Upgrade to soon coming 2010.11 (part 3: rename patches dir)
    - [2010.05] Upgrade to soon coming 2010.11 (part 2: correct faulty patches)
    - [2010.05] Upgrade to soon coming 2010.11 (part 1)
